entries.name: First Time Multisim
entries.details: Notes on logic gates covering the basics of AND, OR, NOT, and XOR operations.
bulletPoints: AND gate produces a high output only if both inputs are high.
OR gate produces a high output if at least one input is high.
XOR gate produces a high output if only one of the inputs is high.

entries.name: Logic Gates Notes
entries.details: Basic notes on digital logic gates.
bulletPoints: AND gate produces high output only if both inputs are high.
OR gate produces high output if any input is high.
